================================================================================
# MODULE : SESSION & CORE (Default, Session, Status)
================================================================================

### Récupération du Token (Password Grant)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api.php/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id={{clientId}}&client_secret={{clientSecret}}&username={{username}}&password={{password}}&scope=api

###

### Vérification de la session
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/session
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Points d'entrée de l'API (Status & Versions)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Découverte des routes v2.3
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

================================================================================
# MODULE : ADMINISTRATION (User, Group, Entity, Profile...)
================================================================================

### Liste des Utilisateurs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Administration/User
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Création d'un Utilisateur (POST) avec TOUS les paramètres
POST {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Administration/User
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "api_user_full",
  "realname": "Nom complet",
  "firstname": "Prénom",
  "password": "api_password_123!",
  "password2": "api_password_123!",
  "phone": "+33100000001",
  "phone2": "+33100000002",
  "mobile": "+33600000003",
  "comment": "Commentaire descriptif",
  "is_active": true,
  "is_deleted": false,
  "location": 1,
  "authtype": 1,
  "default_profile": 1,
  "default_entity": 0,
  "title": 1,
  "category": 1,
  "registration_number": "REG-12345",
  "begin_date": "2024-01-01 10:00:00",
  "end_date": "2025-01-01 10:00:00",
  "nickname": "api_nickname",
  "substitution_start_date": "2024-06-01 10:00:00",
  "substitution_end_date": "2024-06-15 10:00:00"
}

### Obtenir un Utilisateur spécifique (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Administration/User/2
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Mise à jour d'un Utilisateur (PATCH)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Administration/User/2
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "realname": "Nom modifié",
  "is_active": false
}

### Suppression d'un Utilisateur (DELETE)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Administration/User/2
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Liste des Groupes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Administration/Group
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Liste des Entités
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Administration/Entity
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Liste des Profils
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Administration/Profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

================================================================================
# MODULE : ASSETS (Computer, Monitor, Phone, Printer, NetworkEquipment...)
================================================================================

### Liste des Ordinateurs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assets/Computer
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Création d'un Ordinateur (POST) avec TOUS les paramètres
POST {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assets/Computer
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "PC-TEST-API-FULL",
  "comment": "Création exhaustive via API v2.3",
  "status": 1,
  "entity": 0,
  "is_recursive": false,
  "manufacturer": 1,
  "user": 1,
  "user_tech": 2,
  "contact": "John Doe",
  "contact_num": "+33123456789",
  "serial": "SN-123456789",
  "otherserial": "INV-98765",
  "is_deleted": false,
  "location": 1,
  "type": 1,
  "model": 1,
  "group": 1,
  "group_tech": 2,
  "network": 1,
  "autoupdatesystem": 1,
  "is_template": false,
  "template_name": "",
  "is_dynamic": false,
  "ticket_tco": 1500.50
}

### Obtenir un Ordinateur spécifique (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assets/Computer/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Mise à jour d'un Ordinateur (PATCH)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assets/Computer/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "PC-TEST-API-MODIFIED",
  "status": 2
}

### Suppression d'un Ordinateur (DELETE)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assets/Computer/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

