================================================================================
# MODULE : ASSISTANCE (Ticket, Change, Problem)
================================================================================

### Liste des tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assistance/Ticket
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Obtenir un ticket spécifique
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assistance/Ticket/{{itemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Création d'un Ticket (POST) avec TOUS les paramètres
POST {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assistance/Ticket
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Ticket exhaustif de test",
  "content": "&lt;p&gt;Description complète du ticket avec formatage HTML.&lt;/p&gt;",
  "user_recipient": 1,
  "user_editor": 1,
  "is_deleted": false,
  "category": 1,
  "location": 1,
  "urgency": 3,
  "impact": 3,
  "priority": 3,
  "date": "2024-01-01 10:00:00"
}

### Mise à jour d'un Ticket (PATCH)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assistance/Ticket/{{itemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Ticket mis à jour via API",
  "urgency": 4
}

### Suppression d'un Ticket (DELETE)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assistance/Ticket/{{itemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Liste des Changements (Change)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assistance/Change
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Liste des Problèmes (Problem)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api.php/v2.3/Assistance/Problem
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

